This hybrid smartwatch combines timeless analog looks with smart features, such as text messages from your paired smartphone delivered right to your wrist. With a flick of your wrist or a tap of your finger, the stylish patterned lens lights up to reveal a bright touchscreen display that disappears when you’re done with it. And — with a battery that lasts up to 5 days between charges — it really can keep up. Lily must be connected to the Garmin Connect app on your compatible smartphone.
